notesStmt.note: This conversation takes place during the coffee break of a summer school course. S1 and S2 are practising and revising words for the next German class. In between, they are chatting about last night, as S1 went out and does not feel well today. S4 comes later and leaves earlier. At some point they briefly ask S6 and S7, who are sitting at another table, to help them with some words. S8 joins briefly for some comments. Since S1 and S2 are learning and practising or thinking about certain words, they naturally do not always get them right the first time. This transcript also includes such words marked as LN which are 'German by intention' but do not actually exist, so no translation is provided for such words. Whenever there is a translation, it is of an existing German word.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
